---
title: Sesame-Soy Tofu and Rice Bowls with Sriracha Mayo Drizzle
description: This veggie-packed bowl is topped with umami-rich sesame-soy tofu. Fluffy rice and sriracha mayo finish this quick weeknight dinner off with a bang!
